{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-doc-template-js","path":"/docs/raas/intro","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"fields":{"slug":"/docs/raas/intro"},"id":"9c3bb0ba-138a-5549-b5ea-2d7957f887c0","html":"<h1 id=\"personalized-recommendation\"><a href=\"#personalized-recommendation\" aria-label=\"personalized recommendation permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Personalized Recommendation</h1>\n<p>The recommendation engine has state-of-the-art deep learning models that is able to increase sales and revenue by suggesting right products to right users no matter they are new or returning ones. The real-time recommendations are all based on the users' behavior on the website and interactions with products. The deep learning technologies can also solve long-tail products issue and consider the impact from time sequence and external environment which the traditional recommendation engine can’t solve.</p>\n<p>You can follow below sections to have an overview of the recommendation engine:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/raas/intro#system-components\">System Components</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/raas/intro/#core-ai-algorithm\">Core AI Algorithm</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/raas/intro#data-collection\">Data Collection</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/raas/intro#security-and-privacy\">Security and Privacy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/docs/raas/intro#customization\">Customization</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"system-components\"><a href=\"#system-components\" aria-label=\"system components permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>System Components</h2>\n<p>To meet diverse requirements from different e-commerce platforms and to speed up the integration, CHANGING.AI’s personalized product recommendation solution includes the following core components.</p>\n<figure class=\"md-image\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 753px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/238f2fa3cba1402d3f7baac587cfd3dd/d7a05/system-components.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 72.37715803452855%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"system components\" title=\"system components\" src=\"/static/238f2fa3cba1402d3f7baac587cfd3dd/d7a05/system-components.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/238f2fa3cba1402d3f7baac587cfd3dd/47425/system-components.jpg 195w,\n/static/238f2fa3cba1402d3f7baac587cfd3dd/53d89/system-components.jpg 390w,\n/static/238f2fa3cba1402d3f7baac587cfd3dd/d7a05/system-components.jpg 753w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 753px) 100vw, 753px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n</figure>\n<h2 id=\"core-ai-algorithm\"><a href=\"#core-ai-algorithm\" aria-label=\"core ai algorithm permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Core AI Algorithm</h2>\n<p>There has been continuous enhancement of the product recommendation algorithms in the past decade. It started with basic association rule and later to collaborative filtering/matrix factorization based on traditional machine learning. However, there are some limitations cannot be resolved with tradition machine learning and association rule:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>long tail recommendation</li>\n<li>bad recommendation caused by ignorance of purchase sequence</li>\n<li>bad recommendation caused by ignorance of external data</li>\n<li>cold start.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Deep Learning algorithm has significant breakthrough on:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>computer vision to understand/recognize image/videos</li>\n<li>natural language to understand the product description</li>\n<li>Machine Auto Featuring to overcome the limits by traditional human featuring by trial-and-error</li>\n<li>prediction based on time sequence while current algorithm ignores user behaviour sequence.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Our recommendation core algorithms are empowered by deep learning algorithms. With the deep learning breakthroughs, we can solve most of user cases nowaways the online retailers could encounter.</p>\n<h2 id=\"data-collection\"><a href=\"#data-collection\" aria-label=\"data collection permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Data Collection</h2>\n<p>To provide personalized recommendations to the right users, below data is required:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Product catalog</li>\n<li>User-product interactions</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"md-image\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 780px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/8089293b165f320de7b6d95762eb70c7/58539/data-collection.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 44.33701657458564%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"data collection flow\" title=\"data collection flow\" src=\"/static/8089293b165f320de7b6d95762eb70c7/751b3/data-collection.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/8089293b165f320de7b6d95762eb70c7/47425/data-collection.jpg 195w,\n/static/8089293b165f320de7b6d95762eb70c7/53d89/data-collection.jpg 390w,\n/static/8089293b165f320de7b6d95762eb70c7/751b3/data-collection.jpg 780w,\n/static/8089293b165f320de7b6d95762eb70c7/b2d4e/data-collection.jpg 1170w,\n/static/8089293b165f320de7b6d95762eb70c7/58539/data-collection.jpg 1448w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n</figure>\n<p>The product catalog can help the engine to have holistic understanding on product details and user interactions data can help the engine learn how products are related to specific users in specific timeframe so that it could suggest the best-fit recommendation to users.\nFor more details, you can refer to <a href=\"/docs/raas/data-collection\">Data Collection</a> page.</p>\n<h2 id=\"security-and-privacy\"><a href=\"#security-and-privacy\" aria-label=\"security and privacy permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Security and Privacy</h2>\n<p>Consumer behavior, product data and transaction data are all critical and needs to be well taken care of. We will de-identify of the data we collected. We further user encryption to protect the data and provide authorization tool to grant access to people related.</p>\n<h2 id=\"customization\"><a href=\"#customization\" aria-label=\"customization permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Customization</h2>\n<p>Different E-commerce have different strategy and approach to run their business. We provide configuration tools for customer to apply their rule. It includes:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Restrict product recommendation within the same department or not (e.g. only recommend electronics instead of clothes in the electronics department)</li>\n<li>Define the number of recommendation to be displayed per page</li>\n<li>Include specific type of products into recommendation (e.g. during specific event, to recommend the products related to that event more)</li>\n<li>Exclude specific type of products into recommendation. (e.g. merchant wants to exclude certain type of products for their strategy reason).</li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"date":null,"title":"Introduction","sidebar":"Docs","showTitle":false,"hideAnchor":null}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false}}}